summary: School’s coming to an end, and I’ve decided to update my commissions page, go back to normal pricing. I’ll reblog again on this...
caption:
School’s coming to an end, and I’ve decided to update my commissions page, go back to normal pricing. I’ll reblog again on this blog each time a slot is filled and/or when a spot is free after they’ve been filled! I’ll open five ( 5 ) at a time since I am still in school, but I have a month left, and then I’ll be able to open more slots after that! Slots go by how many pieces a person asks for. Example: Someone commissions for two separate pieces, so they get two slots filled.

Will draw:

  • Canon characters ( human, humanoid, aliens, robots, furries/anthro )
  • Original characters ( visual reference needed OR a detailed description )
  • Simplistic robot designs
  • Crossover Interactions

Will not draw:

  • Incest 
  • Pedophilic ships
  • Racist / Sexist / Homophobic / Transphobic content
  • Genderbends / Cis Swaps / Rule 63 
  • Sexual content ( a. because i’m not super comfortable drawing it and b. tumblr won’t allow it )
  • Backgrounds ( unless you pay extra, which price-wise will depend on complexity )

Payments can be made via my paypal: paypal.me/benzystellar or my ko-fi: iaconic

IM me here @benzstellar if you are interested!
